Package <Unnamed>

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Climber
    The Climber class stores information about individual climbers including: name, age, gender and a list of mountains they have climbed.
    ClimberTest
    The test class ClimberTest.
    Club
    The Club class holds information about all climbers in the club including: The Climber within the Club who has recorded the highest average mountain height The highest Mountain recorded by a member of a Club A list of all Mountains that have been recorded, that are higher than a given level
    ClubStats
    The ClubStats class provides methods which allows the user to add a new climber to a club, add details of a mountain to a climber, as well as view statistics about the club, all in a graphical way though printing this information to the console.
    ClubTest
    The test class ClubTest.
    Mountain
    The Mountain class stores the height (m) and name of different mountains
    MountainTest
    The test class MountainTest.
